data.description: Price improvement $389,900 as of 12/6/23. Turn key condo in "Villa Bonita" conveniently located in a gated community of Paradise Hills right next to the 54. Features wall unit air conditioner, upgraded laminate flooring and in unit laundry. Kitchen has beautiful wood cabinetry, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Wood burning fireplace in living room which extends to a balcony with a storage closet. Complex also has spa, tennis court & BBQ areas w/ picnic tables. HOA fee includes water & trash. One covered parking spot. VA APPROVED COMPLEX.
